{"tid":1668966,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「眾望所歸」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-22T09:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T09:44:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5e676285e603c0fd0da82ea284a125b8ea65cc90","tid":1668966,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191022/20791137/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F20791137%2F&d=kAMrkm0lh8tAzahNx%2FKaSNE6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=ddf7d97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191022%2F20791137%2F&h=b1ebbc27\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191022/20791137/</a><br />\n<br />\n「眾望所歸」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191022/large/1571642368_da8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191022%2Flarge%2F1571642368_da8d.jpg&h=113a1f9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n看到一些小朋友的概念圖工作紙造句紙，有提到「為我們服務的人」：消防員、醫生、警察，前2者都得到很高評價，後者印象是「打示威者」、「濫捕」、「暴力」、「催淚彈」。還有造句紙上童稚筆跡：「我既害怕沒有光的黑暗，也害怕不停打人的黑警，更害怕專橫的林鄭月娥。」<br />\n<br />\n童心無詐，童言無忌──看時只覺笑中有淚。曾幾何時，小朋友志願當警察，儆惡懲奸除暴安良，「英雄形象」淪落，百年警譽摧毀，原來只需毒蛾幾個月的縱容姑息獸性大爆發。<br />\n<br />\n我曾撫慰幼稚園小朋友，因外傭姐姐一句再曳就叫警察捉他，忽地悽厲大哭成身顫抖，怕警察射爆眼打到成地血，他的血流晒就會死&hellip;&hellip;現今怕黑警憎黑警的，已自3歲起了。<br />\n<br />\n台灣作家九把刀為小說取材，在fb留言問：「現在社會從事什麼職業最丟臉最可恥？」之前以為是賣假油，原來絕大部份答「香港警察」，眾望所歸。<br />\n<br />\n一回聽人談到其姊妹淘感情波折，說去年聖誕訂婚，今年暑假擺酒，婚期一再延遲最後告吹，女方再愛也不能容忍與無良黑警過一生──其家人還道：「要為下一代着想：將來子女去不到美國&hellip;&hellip;」這才是當頭棒喝！<br />\n<br />\n（本文所指是「黑警」，自問「白警」、「灰警」不必對號入座。但此乃共業。） <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"43cfb8b718820f92844c8e6fd3dad2444ac86eef","tid":1668966,"uid":284119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"成日睇錯左做李桂華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b51ba10a8d0ed182672032ce4289cd4f5aba7c","tid":1668966,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43cfb8b718820f92844c8e6fd3dad2444ac86eef","tid":1668966,"uid":284119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:42:20.000Z","msg":"成日睇錯左做李桂華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T09:44:51.000Z","msg":"邊個係李桂華 ?"}]}